function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	tParticipants = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	for i, idPlayer in pairs(tParticipants) do
		Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idPlayer, sound_ambush_wave)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "spawns")
	iWaves = 1
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	tParticipants = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
		for i, idPlayer in pairs(tParticipants) do
			Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idPlayer, sound_ambush_wave)
		end
		
		Hydra.Wait(1.5)
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "spawns")
		iWaves = 1
end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	
	if iWaves ~=3 then
		tParticipants = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
		for i, idPlayer in pairs(tParticipants) do
			Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idPlayer, sound_ambush_wave)
		end
	
		Hydra.Wait(1.5)
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "spawns")
		iWaves = iWaves + 1
	else
		tParticipants = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
		for i, idPlayer in pairs(tParticipants) do
			Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idPlayer, sound_ambush_boss)
		end
	
		Hydra.Wait(1.5)
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf)
end
